question: Within a radius of 50 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant in the direction of Sequoia Hospital, Redwood City, CA from Golden Gate Bridge Lookout, Sausalito, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.486003 37.82872)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.255023 37.479511)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.486003 37.82872)',4326)::geography, 50000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.486003 37.82872)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
